你能够调用以下的API:
[['SocialSecurity.get_contribution_rate', {'name': 'SocialSecurity.get_contribution_rate', 'description': 'Get the contribution rate and base for social security and housing fund in a specific city.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'city', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the city name'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'contribution_rate', 'description': 'the contribution rate for social security and housing fund.'}, {'name': 'base', 'description': 'the base amount for contribution.'}]}], ['InvestmentPolicy.get_city_policies', {'name': 'InvestmentPolicy.get_city_policies', 'description': 'Get the investment policies in a specific city.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'city', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the city name'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'policies', 'description': 'the list of investment policies in the city.'}]}], ['InvestmentAdvisor.get_personal_advice', {'name': 'InvestmentAdvisor.get_personal_advice', 'description': 'Get personalized investment advice based on age, income, and risk tolerance.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'age', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the age of the investor.'}, {'name': 'income', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the annual income of the investor.'}, {'name': 'risk_tolerance', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the risk tolerance level of the investor (low, medium, high)'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'advice', 'description': 'the personalized investment advice.'}]}], ['RiskAssessment.evaluate_risk', {'name': 'RiskAssessment.evaluate_risk', 'description': 'Evaluate the risk of an investment based on the amount and type.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'investment_amount', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'the amount of money to be invested.'}, {'name': 'investment_type', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the type of investment (stocks, bonds, real estate, etc.)'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'risk_level', 'description': 'the risk level of the investment.'}]}], ['InvestmentGuide.create_guide', {'name': 'InvestmentGuide.create_guide', 'description': 'Create an investment guide based on the investment plan.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'investment_plan', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'the type of investment plan (conservative, balanced, aggressive)'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'guide', 'description': 'the investment guide.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
